         <div>
            <head>"OUR LAND"</head>
            
            <lg>
               <l>We should have a land of sun,</l>
               <l>Of gorgeous sun,</l>
               <l>And a land of fragrant water</l>
               <l>Where the twilight is a soft bandanna handkerchief</l>
               <l>Of rose and gold,</l>
               <l>And not this land</l>
               <l>Where life is cold.</l>
            </lg>
            
            <lg>
               <l>We should have a land of trees,</l>
               <l>Of tall thick trees,</l>
               <l>Bowed down with chattering parrots</l>
               <l>Brilliant as the day,</l>
               <l>And not this land where birds are gray.</l>
            </lg>
            
            <lg>
               <l>Ah, we should have a land of joy,</l>
               <l>Of love and joy and wine and song,</l>
               <l>And not this land where joy is wrong.</l>
            </lg>

            <byline>-Langston Hughes</byline>
         </div>
      </body>
